    <item>
      <title>梅奥表示，银行股将因利率和软着陆而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/mayo-sees-bank-stocks-ready-to-take-off-on-rates-soft-landing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行分析师迈克·梅奥表示，随着美联储准备降低利率，且美国经济几乎没有出现衰退迹象，银行股将迎来强劲上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/mayo-sees-bank-stocks-ready-to-take-off-on-rates-soft-landing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空公司所有者 Abra 接近达成 13 亿美元 Castlelake 贷款协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/airline-owner-abra-nears-1-3-billion-loan-deal-with-castlelake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的巴西航空公司 Gol Linhas Aereas Inteligentes SA 的最大股东即将达成协议，从投资公司 Castlelake LP 筹集 13 亿美元资金，以避免债券违约的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/airline-owner-abra-nears-1-3-billion-loan-deal-with-castlelake</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:05:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
